templateAssets.content:
SDSU offers mirrored programs at SDSU Imperial Valley, located in Calexico, CA. These programs are available through Transfer Success Pathway (TSP), a new program offering guaranteed admission to eligible students.


Due to high demand, admission to SDSU is highly competitive. General admission information is available at:http://arweb.sdsu.edu/es/admissions/transfers/index.html

1. Receive a grade of B (3.0) or better in P H 101 and P H 292 . These courses cannot be taken for credit/no credit (Cr/NC);
  2. Complete each remaining course in preparation for the major with a minimum grade of C. These courses cannot be taken for credit/no credit (Cr/NC)
